        </p>
        <br />
        <br />
        <p>
            Together, we can achieve more. Thank you for being a part of our journey and for making a difference in the lives of others.
        </p>
        <p>
            Your generosity makes the world a brighter place. Join us, and let's create a better future together.
        </p>
        <br />
        <br />
        <p>
            Together, we can build a world where everyone has the opportunity to thrive. Your support makes it possible.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <iframe width="100%" height="500px" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/beMHj0b-UoA?si=MWXQGyZfkJcoUUOn" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
